actualtext: "Finally, my step ggg grandmother was listed by the Winter Quarters Cemetery sexton as Elizabeth King but was born Elizabeth Warriner in Brattleboro, VT. (She later married to a Mr. White, a Mr. Keep and finally to my ggg grandfather Thomas King.  Thomas died in 1844 in Montrose before his wife arrived in Winter Quarters).  Elizabeth Warriner is not listed by her maiden name in any of the available lists or biographies."
